icationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Whose Story Is History?</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7156227\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"Images of Nampeyo, CCC members, Pauline Patraw Mead, and George Murakami.\" src=\"/grca/learn/historyculture/images/MicrosoftTeams-image_18.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"Whose Story Is History?\"/>\n<figcaption>Images of Nampeyo, CCC members, Pauline Patraw Mead, and George Murakami. <p class=\"figcredit\">NPS Photo</p></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7156230\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7156230\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2 paraeid=\"{4986f049-4a99-4167-8d4c-aa6e384720ea}{129}\" paraid=\"1839788361\">Whose Story is History? Bringing the Diverse History of Grand Canyon into the Light </h2>\n<p paraeid=\"{4986f049-4a99-4167-8d4c-aa6e384720ea}{141}\" paraid=\"797161359\"><br/>\nThe stories of marginalized communities often go without recognition and appreciation. Grand Canyon has incredible stories of art, resilience, activism, and courage. The park also has challenging and uncomfortable histories of injustice and exclusion. Exploring all of these stories provides a more complete understanding of Grand Canyon history. Dive into the Whose Story is History Project with articles centered around historically underrepresented narratives and perspectives.  <br/>\n</p>\n<p paraeid=\"{4986f049-4a99-4167-8d4c-aa6e384720ea}{161}\" paraid=\"1890261671\"><em><strong>Why are some legacies preserved and others ignored? How can we give due value to all the voices and perspectives at Grand Canyon? </strong></em></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7156233\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7156233\">\n\n<div class=\"container ListingList ListingResults\" id=\"searchListing-7223E150-B6C1-2DC5-1CA660F325824B7A\">\n<h2>Whose Story Is History Articles</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"results\">\n<a name=\"results\"></a>\n<div class=\"display-list-view\" id=\"display-list-view\">\n<div class=\"info-micro-filter\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<div class=\"result-count\"></div>\n<div class=\"result-selectors\">\n<div class=\"result-facet-Parks_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Parks_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Location\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-parks\">\n<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\n<label for=\"sort-by-select-searchListing-7223E150-B6C1-2DC5-1CA660F325824B7A\">Narrow By Location:</label>\n</span>\n<select multiple=\"\" name=\"result-narrow-Parks_Item\"></select>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result-facet-Organizations_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Organizations_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Office\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-organizations\">\n<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\n<label for=\"sort-by-select-searchListing-7223E150-B6C1-2DC5-1CA660F325824B7A\">Narrow By Office:</label>\n</span>\n<select multiple=\"\" name=\"result-narrow-Organizations_Item\"></select>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result-count-select\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"sort-by\" id=\"result-count-form\"><p><label for=\"result-count-select-searchListing-7223E150-B6C1-2DC5-1CA660F325824B7A\">Show</label><select id=\"result-count-select-searchListing-7223E150-B6C1-2DC5-1CA660F325824B7A\" name=\"result-maxRows\">\n<option value=\"10\">10</option>\n<option value=\"40\">40</option>\n</select></p></form>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result-sort-select\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"sort-by\" id=\"result-sort-form\"><p><label for=\"sort-by-select-searchListing-7223E150-B6C1-2DC5-1CA660F325824B7A\">Sort By:</label><select 